International Minerals andChemical Corp said it is offering 1,500,000 shares of 3.25 dlrConvertible Exchangeable Preferred Stock, Series B.    It said each share of Series B Preferred will beconvertible at any time at the holder's option into the 1.266shares of the company's common and will be exchangeable at thecompany's option on any dividend payment date beginning April15, 1990 for 6-1/2 pct convertible subordinated debentures due2017.    The offering is through Merrill Lynch Capital Markets,Lazard Freres and Co and Shearson Lehman Brothers Inc.     Reuter&#3;